Package edu.cofc.grader

Class Test

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.cofc.grader.Test
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    SingleTestAbstractMethod, TestOutline

    public abstract class Test
extends java.lang.Object
    Test provides an interface for creating different types of Test objects. When extending Test, a @see run() method must be implemented.
